downloadTitle: .NET Rocks! - Building Communities at Dallas TechFest
downloadDescription: Carl and Richard talk with three community leaders in Dallas about building communities, and specifically how you can directly benefit from participating locally.
detailsSection: The Dallas Techfest was held in Addison, TX just outside of Dallas on May 3rd, 2008. For more information go to http://www.dallastechfest.com.
systemRequirementsSection: Presentations are played using the Microsoft Windows Media Player.
installInstructionSection:
- Select "Save this Program to Disk" to copy the download to your machine for installation at a later time.
- Once the file has been downloaded, execute it in order to extract the media file.
